# nested-prefix-entry-before-inner

## Input

```
a {
  d 1
  b {
    c 2
  }
}

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..30
  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..30
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{"
    NEWLINE@3..4 "\n"
    SPACE@4..6 "  "
    ENTRY@6..10
      WORD_KEY@6..7
        WORD@6..7 "d"
      SPACE@7..8 " "
      INTEGER@8..9
        NUMERAL@8..9 "1"
      NEWLINE@9..10 "\n"
    SPACE@10..12 "  "
    PREFIX_BLOCK@12..28
      WORD_KEY@12..13
        WORD@12..13 "b"
      SPACE@13..14 " "
      OPEN_BRACE@14..15 "{"
      NEWLINE@15..16 "\n"
      SPACE@16..20 "    "
      ENTRY@20..24
        WORD_KEY@20..21
          WORD@20..21 "c"
        SPACE@21..22 " "
        INTEGER@22..23
          NUMERAL@22..23 "2"
        NEWLINE@23..24 "\n"
      SPACE@24..26 "  "
      CLOSE_BRACE@26..27 "}"
      NEWLINE@27..28 "\n"
    CLOSE_BRACE@28..29 "}"
    NEWLINE@29..30 "\n"
```

